{"from":"manager","to":"eng-1-1","body":"TASK 7 (CRITICAL PATH): Implement src/movegen.py + tests/test_movegen.py\n\nboard.py and constants.py are now on main. Pull main into your worktree first: git merge main\n\nFiles to create: src/movegen.py, tests/test_movegen.py\n\nFunctions needed in movegen.py:\n- generate_pseudo_legal(board) -> generator of encoded moves (16-bit ints)\n- generate_legal_moves(board) -> list[int] — filter pseudo-legal: make_move, check is_attacked(own king, enemy), unmake_move\n- generate_legal_captures(board) -> list[int] — legal captures only (for quiescence search)\n- perft(board, depth) -> int — count leaf nodes\n\nPseudo-legal generation must handle ALL move types:\n- Pawn: single push, double push (DOUBLE_PAWN flag), captures (CAPTURE flag), en passant (EP_CAPTURE), promotions (PROMO_KNIGHT/BISHOP/ROOK/QUEEN, and PROMO_KNIGHT_CAP/BISHOP_CAP/ROOK_CAP/QUEEN_CAP for captures)\n- Knight: KNIGHT_MOVES[sq] table, QUIET or CAPTURE flag\n- Bishop: walk BISHOP_DIRS rays via RAYS[sq][dir]\n- Rook: walk ROOK_DIRS rays via RAYS[sq][dir]\n- Queen: walk all 8 directions via RAYS[sq][dir]\n- King: KING_MOVES[sq] table, QUIET or CAPTURE flag\n- Castling: CASTLE_KING/CASTLE_QUEEN flags, check castling rights, squares between must be empty, king must not be in check, must not pass through check\n\nLegal filtering: for each pseudo-legal move, board.make_move(move), check if board.is_attacked(board.king_sq[board.turn ^ 1], board.turn), if attacked discard, always board.unmake_move(). Note: after make_move, turn has flipped, so check the PREVIOUS side's king.\n\nREQUIRED PERFT TESTS (these MUST match exactly):\n- Starting pos depth 1 = 20\n- Starting pos depth 2 = 400\n- Starting pos depth 3 = 8902\n- Starting pos depth 4 = 197281\n- Kiwipete (r3k2r/p1ppqpb1/bn2pnp1/3PN3/1p2P3/2N2Q1p/PPPBBPPP/R3K2R w KQkq -) depth 1 = 48, depth 2 = 2039, depth 3 = 97862\n\nAdditional tests:\n- EP moves generated correctly\n- Castling generated when legal, blocked when not\n- Promotions generate all 4 piece types\n- Pinned pieces restricted\n- Moves that resolve check\n\nRun: python -m pytest tests/test_movegen.py -v\n\nImport from src.constants and src.board. See CLAUDE.md for all signatures.","msg_type":"assign","timestamp":1773174260}